tagged literals
--- --- ---

test 'tagged literal', fn:
  expect cps_expr fn:
    10sec

  | equals_fink fn:
    ·load ·scope, ·id'sec', fn sec, ·scope:
      ·apply sec, 10, ·state, fn ·v_0, ·state:
